HEADWORD: Soyle
<hw>Soyle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Aphetic form of
<ets>assoil</ets>.]</ety> <def>To solve, to clear up; <as>as, to
<ex>soyl</ex> all other texts</as>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Tyndate.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

